t;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; clear: left; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3. 相机</h3><p style=\"margin-top: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 1.4em; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">使用场景/目的：用于完成二维码扫描等需要使用该权限的相关功能</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 1.4em; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">收集个人信息的类型：图像</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 1.4em; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">拒绝授权的后果：无法写入、读取本地相册</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 1.4em; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p><br/></p>', '1691396762');
