信息</span></span></p></td><td valign=\"center\" style=\"border-left: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; border-top: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext;padding:5px 10px;\"><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"color:#333333;letter-spacing:0;font-style:normal;font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;Heiti SC Light&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-family:Heiti SC Light;\">根据用户的搜索、</span> <span style=\"font-family:Heiti SC Light;\">浏览等需求进行相应展示</span></span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height:56px\"><td valign=\"center\" style=\"border-left: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; border-top: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext;padding:5px 10px;\"><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"color:#333333;letter-spacing:0;font-style:normal;font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;Heiti SC Light&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-family:Heiti SC Light;\">实名认证</span></span><span style=\"color:#333333;letter-spacing:0;font-style:normal;font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;Heiti SC Light&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-family:Heiti SC Light;\">/身份核验</span></span></p></td><td valign=\"center\" style=\"border-left: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; border-top: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext;padding:5px 10px;\"><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"color:#333333;letter-spacing:0;font-style:normal;font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;Heiti SC Light&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-family:Heiti SC Light;\">姓名、身份证号、银行卡号、手机号、人脸验证</span></span></p></td><td valign=\"center\" style=\"border-left: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; border-top: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext;padding:5px 10px;\"><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"color:#333333;letter-spacing:0;font-style:normal;font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;Heiti SC Light&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-family:Heiti SC Light;\">用于进行账号的实名认证操作或出于账号安全用于身份核验</span><span style=\"font-family:Heiti SC Light;\">,您可自主选择认证或核验的方式</span></span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height:56px\"><td valign=\"center\" style=\"border-left: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; border-top: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext;padding:5px 10px;\"><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"color:#333333;letter-spacing:0;font-style:normal;font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;Heiti SC Light&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-family:Heiti SC Light;\">支付</span>/提现</span></p></td><td valign=\"center\" style=\"border-left: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; border-top: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext;padding:5px 10px;\"><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"color: #333333; letter-spacing: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.58em;font-family: &quot;Heiti SC Light&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family:Heiti SC Light;\">支付宝帐号、微信账号、银行卡信息</span></span></p></td><td valign=\"center\" style=\"border-left: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; border-top: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext;padding:5px 10px;\"><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"color: #333333; letter-spacing: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.58em;font-family: &quot;Heiti SC Light&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family:Heiti SC Light;\">用于您支付或提现的目的使用</span></span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height:56px\"><td valign=\"center\" style=\"border-left: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; border-top: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext;padding:5px 10px;\"><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"color:#333333;letter-spacing:0;font-style:normal;font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;Heiti SC Light&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-family:Heiti SC Light;\">设备信息</span></span></p></td><td valign=\"center\" style=\"border-left: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; border-top: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext;padding:5px 10px;\"><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0\"><span style=\"color: #333333; letter-spacing: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.58em;font-family: &quot;Heiti SC Light&quot;;\"></span><span style=\"color: #333333; letter-spacing: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.58em;font-family: &quot;Heiti SC Light&quot;;\">IMEI、MAC、AndroidID、OAID、IDFA、OpenUDID、GUID、SIM卡IMSI、ICCID、IP、软件安装列表</span></p></td><td valign=\"center\" style=\"border-left: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; border-top: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext;padding:5px 10px;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #333333;               text-decoration-thickness: initial;   vertical-align: inherit; font-size: 14px;font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px;font-family: &quot;Heiti SC Light&quot;;\">IMEI、MAC、AndroidID、OAID、IDFA、OpenUDID、GUID、SIM卡IMSI、ICCID、IP：基于设备信息生成脱敏的终端用户设备唯一性标识，以确保提供 SDK 服务；</span><br/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #333333;               text-decoration-thickness: initial;   vertical-align: inherit; font-size: 14px;font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"color: #333333; letter-spacing: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.58em;font-family: &quot;Heiti SC Light&quot;;\">软件安装列表：为了预防病毒、木马程序或其他恶意程序、网站，我们可能会收集你设备安装的应用信息、正在运行的进程信息或设备内存中寄存的数据，以防止你的个人信息泄露</span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height:56px\"><td valign=\"center\" style=\"border-left: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; border-top: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext;padding:5px 10px;\"><p style=\"text-align:left;;\"><span style=\"color:#333333;letter-spacing:0;font-style:normal;font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;Heiti SC Light&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-family:Heiti SC Light;\">移动位置</span></span></p></td><td valign=\"center\" style=\"border-left: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; border-top: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext;padding:5px 10px;\"><p style=\"text-align:left;;\"><span style=\"color: #333333; letter-spacing: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.58em;font-family: &quot;Heiti SC Light&quot;;\">包括经纬度、GNSS信息、WiFi网关地址、BSSID、SSID、WiFi信号强度、WiFi状态、WiFi参数、WiFi列表、基站ID数据信息、运营商信息、设备信号强度信息、IP地址、蓝牙信息和传感器信息（加速度，陀螺仪、方向、压力、旋转矢量、光照、磁力计）</span></p></td><td valign=\"center\" style=\"border-left: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; border-top: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext;padding:5px 10px;\"><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;background:#ffffff\"><span style=\"color: #333333; letter-spacing: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.58em;font-family: &quot;Heiti SC Light&quot;;\">为了返回骑手的精确或粗略位置信息，方便用户查看骑手移动位置路径和显示移动方向。其中传感器信息仅在隧道等特定连续定位场景使用，用来为您提供持续定位服务。</span><br/></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height:56px\"><td valign=\"center\" style=\"border-left: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; border-top: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext;padding:5px 10px;\"><p style=\"text-align:left;;\"><span style=\"color:#333333;letter-spacing:0;font-style:normal;font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;Heiti SC Light&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-family:Heiti SC Light;\">附加信息</span></span></p></td><td valign=\"center\" style=\"border-left: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; border-top: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext;padding:5px 10px;\"><p style=\"text-align:left;;\"><span style=\"color:#333333;letter-spacing:0;font-style:normal;font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;Heiti SC Light&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-family:Heiti SC Light;\">附加信息</span></span></p></td><td valign=\"center\" style=\"border-left: 1px solid windowtext; border-right: 1px solid windowtext; border-top: none; border-bottom: 1px solid windowtext;padding:5px 10px;\"><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;background:#ffffff\"><span style=\"color:#333333;letter-spacing:0;font-style:normal;font-size:19px;background:#ffffff;font-family:&#39;Heiti SC Light&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-family:Heiti SC Light;\">相机：扫码</span></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p><br/></p></section><section class=\"_135editor\" data-role=\"paragraph\"><p><br/></p></section></section>', '1691396872');
